org.at4j.archive.builder

Interface EntityToArchiveFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectoryETAF, EntityTypeETAF, FalseETAF, FileETAF, NameETAF, NameGlobETAF, TrueETAF

    public interface EntityToArchiveFilter
    This is a marker interface for all Filter :s for EntryToArchive objects so that they should be easier to find in the Javadocs. No programs should ever use this.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Karl Gustafsson
